name: PixelFem #13 - Kamala Harris
description:
In 2020, Kamala Harris was elected vice-president of the United States, the first time in history that a woman, and a woman of colour, has been elected to such a position in the White House. Harris, 56, embodies the future of a country that is growing more racially diverse, even if the person voters picked for the top of the ticket was a 77-year-old white man.

✺This work is part of PixelFems, an evolving project on the Tezos blockchain celebrating iconic women from the past and present✺
